    "description": "MareScape is a challenging 2D platformer that will make you question your sanity! Navigate through unforgiving obstacles, fight your muscle memory, and try not to succumb to raging frustration.<br><br>You find yourself wandering through a dark, moonlit forest when you arrive at a strange house. Do you dare enter? Who built this strange house? The only way out of this nightmare is to delve further inside...<br><br>Will you escape the nightmare?<br><br><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong><br><br><u>Unforgiving obstacles</u><br> - Navigate your way past 10 challenging obstacles to escape the nightmare. You will die hundreds of times!<br><br><u>Stylized 2D graphics</u><br> - MareScape offers a modern retrogames feel, with stylized 2D graphics.<br><br><u>Simple controls</u><br> - You control the character with A &amp; D, or the left or right arrow keys, and spacebar. Pause the game with the Escape key.<br><br><u>Time and deaths tracking</u><br> - The game tracks your gameplay time and number of deaths. Challenge your friends to see who can beat the game with the fewest deaths!<br><br><u>Replayability</u><br> - Challenge yourself again to beat the game in the shortest time possible!<br><br><u>Steam Acheivements</u><br> - Unlock Steam Acheivements by beating each obstacle.",
